README.md

Awesome

     A curated list of resources on
     [https://www.terraform.io/]HashiCorp's Terraform.
     [https://terraform.io/][68747470733a2f2f7261776769742e636f6d2f736875
     6169626979792f617765736f6d652d7465727261666f726d2f6d61737465722f7465
     727261666f726d2e737667] Your
     [https://github.com/shuaibiyy/awesome-terraform/blob/master/contribu
     ting.md]contributions are welcome!

   Terraform enables you to safely and predictably create, change, and
   improve production infrastructure. It is an open source tool that
   codifies APIs into declarative configuration files that can be shared
   amongst team members, treated as code, edited, reviewed, and versioned.

Contents

     * Official Resources
     * Community
     * Books
     * Tutorials and Blog Posts
     * Community Modules
