Official Resources

     * [https://www.terraform.io/intro/]Introduction to Terraform
     * [https://www.terraform.io/docs/]Terraform Documentation

Community

     * [https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/terraform-tool]Terraform
       Google Group
     * [https://gitter.im/hashicorp-terraform]Terraform Gitter
     * [https://github.com/hashicorp/terraform/issues]Terraform Bug
       Tracker
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules]Terraform Community
       Modules
     * [https://registry.terraform.io/]Terraform Module Registry

Books

     * [http://www.terraformupandrunning.com/?ref=gruntwork-blog-comprehen
       sive-terraform]Terraform: Up & Running
     * [https://terraformbook.com/]The Terraform Book
     * [https://www.amazon.com/Getting-Started-Terraform-Kirill-Shirinkin/
       dp/1786465108/]Getting Started with Terraform
     * [http://shop.oreilly.com/product/0636920039297.do]Infrastructure as
       Code

Tutorials and Blog Posts

     * [https://blog.agilebits.com/2018/01/25/terraforming-1password/]Terr
       aforming 1Password - How 1Password migrated from CloudFormation to
       Terraform.
     * [https://segment.com/blog/the-segment-aws-stack/]The Segment AWS
       Stack - Shows the behind the scenes of the infrastructure powered
       by Terraform that solved
       [https://segment.com/blog/the-million-dollar-eng-problem/]The
       Million Dollar Engineering Problem at
       [https://segment.com/]Segment.
     * [https://blog.gruntwork.io/a-comprehensive-guide-to-terraform-b3d32
       832baca#.w9x897ywp]A Comprehensive Guide to Terraform - Series of
       blog posts from the author of "Terraform: Up & Running" that guide
       the reader from beginning with Terraform to using it in the real
       world.
     * [http://chiefy.github.io/easily-deploy-a-seneca-microservice-to-ecs
       -with-wercker-and-terraform-part-i/]Easily Deploy A Seneca
       Microservice to ECS with Wercker and Terraform: Part I,
       [http://chiefy.github.io/easily-deploy-a-seneca-microservice-to-ecs
       -with-wercker-and-terraform-part-ii/]II &
       [http://chiefy.github.io/easily-deploy-a-seneca-microservice-to-ecs
       -with-wercker-and-terraform-part-i/]III - Illustrates how Terraform
       can be incorporated into a microservice deployment pipeline.
     * [http://www.stratoscale.com/blog/openstack/tutorial-how-to-use-terr
       aform-to-deploy-openstack-workloads/]Tutorial: How to Use Terraform
       to Deploy OpenStack Workloads - Illustrates how easy it is to use
       the OpenStack Terraform provider to deploy a web server.
     * [https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/apn/terraform-beyond-the-basics-with-
       aws/]Terraform: Beyond the Basics with AWS - Explanation of a demo
       using Terraform to provision a sample AWS architecture.
     * [https://www.hashicorp.com/blog/terraform-discourse.html]Deploying
       Discourse with Terraform - Shows how Terraform can create a running
       instance of Discourse on DigitalOcean in one command.
     * [http://vilkeliskis.com/blog/2016/02/10/bootstrapping-docker-with-t
       erraform.html]Bootstrapping Docker Infrastructure With Terraform -
       Walkthrough of deploying a dockerized app on ECS using Terraform.
     * [https://charity.wtf/2016/02/23/two-weeks-with-terraform/]Two Weeks
       with Terraform - Some hard-earned experience from using Terraform
       in the wild, and some operational wisdom.
     * [https://dev.to/koenighotze/using-terraform-for-cloud-deployments--
       -part-1]Using Terraform for Cloud Deployments - Part 1 - Beginner
       tutorial with a focus on using Terraform to provision an EC2
       instance.
     * [https://charity.wtf/2016/03/30/terraform-vpc-and-why-you-want-a-tf
       state-file-per-env/]Terraform, VPC, and why you want a tfstate file
       per env - Some gotchas surrounding using Terraform in large
       projects with multiple environments and how to avoid them.
     * [https://jamesmckay.net/2016/09/sharing-data-between-terraform-conf
       igurations/]Sharing data between Terraform configurations -
       Illustrates how to use remote state to share data between Terraform
       configurations.
     * [https://medium.com/@kief/https-medium-com-kief-using-pipelines-to-
       manage-environments-with-infrastructure-as-code-b37285a1cbf5]Using
       Pipelines to Manage Environments with Infrastructure as Code -
       Explains different approaches for building a pipeline to handle
       infrastructure changes moving from one environment to the next.

Community Modules

   For more Community Modules not listed here please see the
   [https://registry.terraform.io/]Terraform Module Registry.
     * [https://github.com/segmentio/stack]segmentio/stack - Configures
       production infrastructure with AWS, Docker, and ECS.
     * [https://github.com/shuaibiyy/terraform-ecs-jenkins]terraform-ecs-j
       enkins - Provisions Jenkins on AWS ECS using Terraform.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_bastion_s3_k
       eys]tf_aws_bastion_s3_keys - Creates bastion hosts on AWS EC2.
     * [https://github.com/sjevs/terraform-static-website-s3-cloudfront]te
       rraform-static-website-s3-cloudfront - Creates static websites on
       AWS S3 & Cloudfront based on variables.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_vpc_only]tf_
       aws_vpc_only - Provides only VPC (without subnets) in AWS.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_asg_elb]tf_a
       ws_asg_elb - Creates Auto-Scaling Groups and Launch Configurations
       for use with an Elastic Load Balancer.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_availability
       _zones_cfn]tf_aws_availability_zones_cfn - Gets availability zones
       for your AWS region/account from Cloudformation.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_ubuntu_ami]t
       f_aws_ubuntu_ami - Easy way to lookup Ubuntu AMIs with Terraform.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_sg]tf_aws_sg
       - Collection of common security group settings.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_coreos_ami]t
       f_aws_coreos_ami - Easy way to lookup CoreOS AMIs with terraform.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_private_subn
       et_nat_gateway]tf_aws_private_subnet_nat_gateway - Creates private
       subnets with NAT Gateway in AWS.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-aws-modules/terraform-aws-rds]tf_aws_
       rds - Creates RDS resources on AWS.
     * [https://github.com/azavea/terraform-aws-postgresql-rds]terraform-a
       ws-postgresql-rds - Creates PostgreSQL on RDS.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_vpc]tf_aws_v
       pc - Provides VPCs in AWS.
     * [https://github.com/terraform-community-modules/tf_aws_nat]tf_aws_n
       at - NAT instances for AWS.
     * [https://github.com/lunagt/rancher-terraform-digitalocean]rancher-t
       erraform-digitalocean - Rancher server on digitalocean.
     * [https://github.com/cloudposse/terraform-aws-ecr]terraform-aws-ecr
       - Manage Docker container registries on AWS ECR.

Tools

     * [https://github.com/hootsuite/atlantis]Atlantis - Unified workflow
       for collaborating on Terraform through GitHub.
     * [https://github.com/segmentio/terraform-docs]terraform-docs - Quick
       utility to generate docs from terraform modules.
     * [https://github.com/ciscocloud/terraform.py]terraform.py - Ansible
       dynamic inventory script for parsing Terraform state files.
     * [https://github.com/shuaibiyy/terraform-provisioner]terraform-provi
       sioner - Tool for managing multiple provisions of the same
       Terraform scripts.
     * [https://github.com/MastodonC/terraboot]terraboot - DSL to generate
       a terraform configuration and run it.
     * [https://github.com/russellcardullo/terraform-provider-pingdom]terr
       aform-provider-pingdom - Terraform provider to manage pingdom
       resources.
     * [https://github.com/gruntwork-io/terragrunt]terragrunt - Terragrunt
       is a thin wrapper for Terraform that supports locking for Terraform
       state and enforces best practices.
     * [https://github.com/kamatama41/tfenv]tfenv - Terraform version
       manager inspired by rbenv.
     * [https://github.com/coinbase/terraform-landscape]terraform-landscap
       e - Improve Terraform's plan output to be easier to read and
       understand.
     * [https://github.com/28mm/blast-radius]Blast Radius - Interactive
       visualizations of Terraform dependency graphs.

Talks

     * [https://www.infoq.com/presentations/terraform-consul]Orchestrating
       Containers with Terraform and Consul - Mitchell Hashimoto shows how
       Terraform can be used to deploy and scale containerized workloads.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cG7pcksTAnY]Building Scalable,
       Repeatable Infrastructure in the Cloud with Terraform -
       Demonstrates how Terraform enables the practice of Infrastructure
       as Code by deploying TeamCity in AWS using a hosted PostgreSQL.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wgzgVm7Sqlk]Evolving Your
       Infrastructure with Terraform - CTO of OpenCredo provides an
       extensive look at using Terraform in the real-world with the help
       of some interesting use-cases.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=e42A4aBZUkQ]Going Multi-Cloud with
       Terraform and Nomad
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3JVGSq7QIS0]Running a Terraform
       Environment at Scale - Running Terraform at scale with hundreds of
       AWS accounts.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cHrOXPatFeg]Terraforming the
       Composable World - Integrating Terraform with an on-premise bare
       metal provisioning.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ar1PF5iDtbg]State of Terraform
       Providerland - How Terraform providers work and how to write one.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OH6iDKaXpZs]Untangling Terraform
       Through Refactoring - How to refactor your Terraform code in a
       careful way with minimum risk.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RldRDryLiXs]Terraform At Scale -
       How Segment uses Terraform.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CPI6W3LK0-g]Production ChaosMonkey
       with Terraform - How DigitalOcean uses Terraform to run production
       integration tests.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p2ESyuqPw1A]Terraform w/ Lee Trout
       - Focuses on development patterns and how to effectively structure
       Terraform code.
     * [https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=adzqsywrJKk]Webinar: Multi-Cloud,
       One Command with Terraform - Provisioning hybrid cloud
       infrastructure using Terraform.

